title: Lone Ranger TV Show Eps 07-13
description: This is episodes 7 through 13 of the original TV show. Each of these episodes is an avi format video. Also, there is another fella with some of the same earlier episodes who just posted up. These 7  episodes are ripped from DVD so they may be missing a minute of two that would probably be complete from the VHS versions. I don't know why they do that, but sometimes they trim the shows a bit when they release sets on DVD. Anyway, just want to make people aware of the different options.
